markets.title: What will AMD, Inc. say on their next earnings call?
markets.rules_primary: If Reddit is said by any AMD, Inc. representative during the earnings call (including the Q+A) for next, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: Audio of the earnings call will be used to resolve the market. The exact phrase/word, or a plural or possessive form of the phrase/word, must be used. Grammatical/tense inflections are otherwise not included. Hyphenated or compound words used with Reddit will not be included.
